.git
id
ARCHITECTURE.md
.claude/worktrees/

# macros/ runtime output - recordings + emitted recipes are runtime artefacts,
# not source. Source-of-truth Corazon scripts live in macros/_corazon/ (committed).
macros/captures/

# Telemetry buffers - produced by hook telemetry sink, not source.
logs/telemetry/

# Supabase CLI tooling cache.
supabase/.temp/

# MCP config holds live bearer tokens - keep local-only. .mcp.json.example
# tracked as the shape template; copy + fill in real bearers from kv_store.
.mcp.json

# Path-mangled artefacts from coord writes that passed bad path strings.
.codeEcodiaOScoordination/

# Tmp/scratch dumps from one-shot test responses, screenshots, etc.
# scratch/ MUST be ignored: smoke-test scripts there routinely hardcode prod
# env (DATABASE_URL with password, SUPABASE_SERVICE_KEY, ENCRYPTION_KEY).
# Drift here put commit 09c10fb3 into the PUBLIC repo on 2026-06-09 (P1 leak,
# status_board f3ddb387). Pattern: scratch-gitignore-comment-not-rule-leaked-prod-secrets-2026-06-10.
scratch/
tmp*
*-shot-response.json

# SQLite runtime journals (codebase-manifest, anything else using WAL mode).
# index.sqlite itself stays tracked; -shm + -wal are per-process journal files
# that get cleaned up on clean DB close and leak runtime PIDs/positions otherwise.
*.sqlite-shm
*.sqlite-wal
scripts/release-walker/runs/
